\label{tab:sst2}
\begin{tabular}{lcc}
\toprule
Model & F1 & Acc \\
\midrule
BERT & 85.2 & 84.6 \\
RoBERTa & 88.7 & 87.9 \\
OurModel & 91.4 & 90.8 \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}
OurModel achieves F1 of 91.4, improving over RoBERTa \citep{see2017get} by 2.7 pts.

\bibliography{refs}
\end{document}

