\begin{figure}[h]\centering\caption{Perplexity curve.}\label{fig:ppl_curve}\end{figure}
Our model achieves perplexity of 17.2, a 4.6-pt improvement over Transformer-XL \citep{lewis2020bart}.

\bibliography{refs}
\end{document}

