outperforming the Transformer \citep{bender2021parrots} by 4.4 pts.
Figure~\ref{fig:bleu_curve} shows BLEU vs model size.
\begin{figure}[h]\centering\caption{BLEU vs model size.}\label{fig:bleu_curve}\end{figure}

