SpanBERT-large & 79.6 & 78.9 \\
Ours & 82.4 & 81.7 \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}
Ours achieves F1 of 82.4 on CoNLL-2012.
Figure~\ref{fig:coref_eg} shows a coreference example.
\begin{figure}[h]\centering\caption{Coreference example.}\label{fig:coref_eg}\end{figure}

