\section*{Limitations}

\section{Introduction}
Text classification is a fundamental NLP task.
Following \citet{lewis2020bart} and \citet{li2021prefix}, we propose OurModel.
Our model achieves an F1 of 91.4 on SST-2.

\section{Model}
