RoBERTa & 88.7 & 87.9 \\
OurModel & 91.4 & 90.8 \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}
OurModel achieves F1 of 91.4, improving over RoBERTa \citep{see2017get} by 2.7 pts.

